description:
TREASURY/25/1 Ashford Borough Council is looking to procure Treasury Management Specialist Advice Services.  The services will cover;
4.1.1	providing investment advice;
4.1.2	providing interest rate and economic forecasts and assistance for the formulation of an in house investment strategy;
4.1.3	identify a client manager who will facilitate regular strategy meetings and act as a key point of contact with the Council;
